(10, 'Meesaiya murukku', '2', 'Hiphop Tamizha\'s Meesaya Murukku is all set to release tomorrow (21st July). The film made its headlines a few months ago for the song Saitji Saitji.\r\n \r\n\r\nA section of people filed a case and requested the makers to remove the song, or change the lyric, as they felt that those words hurt their sentiments. As a result, Sundar.C and Hiphop Tamizha Adhi decided to take down the song from YouTube.\r\n \r\n\r\nNow, the team has released a new promo song, by changing the lyrics. Saitji has now been replaced by the word, Greatji, and it is expected to feature in the film.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FBxZ44qyPwg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FBxZ44qyPwg', 'video', 'on', 6, 1, 1, '', 'on', 'on'),
(11, 'Neethane Mersal movie', '2', 'The second single from Mersal, Neethanae, a melody, has released and here is our brief review of the song.\r\n \r\n\r\nFirst things first, the biggest soul of the song is the beautiful voices of Rahman and Shreya Ghoshal; their voice gives life to the song. The usage of Carnatic instruments in the interludes are enjoyable and impressive, which is very fresh and gives a new flavour to the song. Vivek\'s lyrics are neat and conveys love, but a section of an audience might find that the lines in the charanam could\'ve been explored more with different lines.\r\n\r\n\r\nHowever, the song is definitely a treat for all music lovers, and the song would slowly grow on you.  With Atlee\'s spectacular picturization, we can expect the song to be breezy and colourful while watching it on the silver screens.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fWajtP80g54', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fWajtP80g54', 'video', 'on', 5, 1, 1, '', 'on', 'on'),
(12, 'sodakku mela sodakku', '2', '#Sodakku by Anirudh from Suriyaâ€™s #ThaanaaSerndhaKoottam is unlike any other Kuthu number before, with Anthony Daasan delivering a performance that only he can. The lyrics by Mani Amuthavan  and Vignesh ShivN talks about boldly questioning corruption. Catch this cult hit right away!', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pn6M7_L1JbQ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pn6M7_L1JbQ', 'video', 'on', 4, 1, 1, '', 'on', 'on'),
(13, 'Hey Pillagaada', '2', 'Watch &amp; Enjoy Hey Pillagaada Full Video Song From Fidaa Movie.Starring Varun Tej, Sai Pallavi, Music composed by Shakthikanth Karthick, Directed by Shekar Kammula and Produced by Dil Raju and Shirish and Co Produced by Harshith Reddy under the Banner of Sri Venkateswara Creations.\r\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k9DMXBFHEH4', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k9DMXBFHEH4', 'video', 'on', 3, 1, 1, '', 'on', 'on'),
