(443, 1, '2018-01-24 08:59:26', '2018-01-24 08:59:26', 'D.Imman, the music composer known for several melodies and albums celebrates his birthday today (January 24). The composer got his major entry into Tamil films through Tamizhan starring actor Vijay and has formed a niche for himself ever since he made his entry.\r\n\r\nHis albums have consistently attracted the masses and the speed with which he completes his music albums is astonishing. In fact, his latest album Tik Tik Tik starring Jayam Ravi marks his landmark 100th film. Completing 100 films and still going strong with the support and love of his fans, we wish D.Imman a very happy birthday and also wish him the best of luck for his upcoming albums.', 'D.Imman celebrates his birthday', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'd-imman-celebrates-his-birthday', '', '', '2018-01-24 09:04:03', '2018-01-24 09:04:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/filmscircle/?p=443', 0, 'post', '', 0),
